Breeze-icons is a freedesktop.org compatible icon theme. It's developed by the KDE Community as part of KDE Frameworks 5 and it's used by default in KDE Plasma 5 and KDE Applications.

Breeze is licensed under GNU LGPLv2.1, please refer to https://invent.kde.org/frameworks/breeze-icons for more detailed information.
Precompiled rcc files are included for convenience to provide icons for the Windows build.
